---------
+CALEDONIA PLASMA THEME
------------------------

Minimalistic dark theme. Original parts, changes, mixes, re-mixes and re-designs by Malcer <malcer@gmx.com> <http://malcer.deviantart.com/> 

Caledonia Plasma-KDE Theme are licensed under the Creative Commons BY-SA.

